Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN导弹齐射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他们火力不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没能破坏到Memento Mori的共振部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少校！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是电磁场光共振部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如其名  进行狙击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认卫星兵器被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密维持现速  脱离此宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通知OO-Raizer撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退命令收到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  援军吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的掩护…是红色的激光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拟太阳炉搭载型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样中东就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那一点都不漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是战争的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它留到你们的时代去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:22:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该留给下一个时代的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星坠落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是Celestial Being干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈裘里…潘·哈裘里上校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了  俄罗斯的暴熊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未能与普特利麦奥斯汇合的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于在某处与计划执行者见面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「听到歌声」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的歌声  沁人肺腑
